This sample hook shows a few metadata for picture files

Prerequisite
------------------------------------
- metadata_ts (https://typo3.org/extensions/repository/view/metadata_ts/current/)


How to use
------------------------------------
- Copy content of setup.txt into your template TS.
- Add this to typo3conf/localconf.php:

$GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['EXTCONF']['file_list']['extraItemMarkerHook'][] = 'EXT:file_list/Samples/metadata/tx_filelist_metadata.php:tx_filelist_metadata';

- Add a plugin to your page and choose a directory containing .JPG pictures from your digital camera
